024 02:58:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-14/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-nazi-who-built-israel-a-nuclear-reactor/00000190-1454-df06-adb8-74d63c4b0000</guid></item><item><title>国际刑事法院检察官卡里姆·汗进行了一场赌博，这将决定以色列人和巴勒斯坦人的未来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-14/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/icc-prosecutor-karim-khans-gamble-will-determine-israelis-and-palestinians-future/00000190-140d-d621-abfa-5f3dcb610000</link><description>国际刑事法院检察官指控以色列领导人在加沙实行饥饿政策，但他要证明自己的观点并不容易。可汗面临的挑战是弥合言论与现实之间的差距</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 01:18:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-14/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/icc-prosecutor-karim-khans-gamble-will-determine-israelis-and-palestinians-future/00000190-140d-d621-abfa-5f3dcb610000</guid></item></channel></rss>